  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help us ensure that we have all the resources to support 240 children and adults with disabilities in 2021.  The COVID-19 pandemic has meant that we face a reduction in our usual funding sources.  With positive cases rising in Sri Lanka once again and local lockdowns in place, we don&apos;t expect our situation to return to &apos;normal&apos; any time soon.  This project aims to fill the funding gap and keep everyone safe and well.</narrative>
  </description>
